      *                  * Pathname del file in input                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ind-eml-000      thru acc-ind-eml-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
       acc-ric-sel-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Oggetto                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ogg-msg-000      thru acc-ogg-msg-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-100.
       acc-ric-sel-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Testo                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tst-msg-000      thru acc-tst-msg-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-200.
       acc-ric-sel-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
